{"tid":2453570,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"自己整過一次牛丸，真係番唔到轉頭","createTime":"2021-03-19T14:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T02:10:52.000Z","uid":392377,"like":106,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"15c31625e1271e900e90065e6956cc30e7d49c53","tid":2453570,"uid":392377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eVQyp9tgGGE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeVQyp9tgGGE&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2Bc2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=4487ab66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eVQyp9tgGGE</a><br />\n食物來講呢<br />\n係好值得一試<br />\n我第一次食自己整既牛丸係都幾震憾<br />\n從未食過咁有牛味既牛丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哩個已經係簡化咗既方法（正宗應該係買舊shank/shin番來打）<br />\n但都已經好食過超市個啲好多好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s6ENOEo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs6ENOEo.png&h=c73042d1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NXSZL3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NXSZL3.png&h=e7aaea72&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打小人嗰部分，就好似豬柳強條片咁，香港人明就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCkdKcJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCkdKcJ.png&h=8a97c050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鐘意就subscribe啊，like啊個啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為牛丸又係啲好人好者唔會走去search來整既嘢<br />\n同埋有半條片都係得香港人先明（英文字幕都唔知點上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\nInstagram (主要係啲post平時煮啲嘢啊 / 同煮食channel有dd關係既無聊story）: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/cooking.therapy1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcooking.therapy1%2F&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2